They use this navigation framework - https://voyager.adriel.cafe/
Let's use it to follow along, then remove it and rely on standard androidx.navigation.

-Remove voyager library in favour of regular navigation framework
See: https://github.com/joelkanyi/FocusBloom/issues/141

Unidirectional data flow (UDF): State flows down (State -> UI), Events flow up (UI -> State)

